name: DATA-2883 - basicpolicy - ACX Table Profiling
description:
This profiling task is to analyze the 'basicpolicy' table from Guidewire (ACX). DATA-2883 is an epic about the refactoring of the DataWarehouse at Andover, specifically about the design and development of the 'Risk' domain.
This analysis is conducted on the first 134k rows (1.5%) of the data.
